# TITAN XAU AI — Cursor IDE Rules
# Yeh file Cursor IDE ko batati hai ki project ke rules kya hain.

## Project Overview
TITAN XAU AI is an institutional-grade AI trading system for XAUUSD (Gold/USD).
3 AI models (XGBoost + LSTM + Transformer) in an ensemble, supervised by CEO module.
Goal: Competition Validation Status with REAL data only (no synthetic).

## STRICT PROHIBITIONS
- NO synthetic data (zero tolerance)
- NO random walk expansion or calibration of small datasets
- NO new architecture — use existing codebase only
- NO new modules — extend existing files only
- NO assumptions — measure everything
- NO synthetic success metrics — only real measured results

## MANDATORY RULES
- CPU-only, fully offline (no paid APIs, no cloud)
- All files under /home/z/my-project/
- Scripts saved to scripts/ before execution (no inline scripts >10 lines)
- Deliverables to download/ (PDF/DOCX/JSON)
- Single worklog at worklog.md (append-only)
- Match user's language (English for English, Hindi for Hindi)
- Update project_memory.md after major tasks

## ARCHITECTURE RULES
- RL NOT in CEO layer (Bayesian + MAB + statistical detectors only)
- RL only in M12 Trade Manager (position scaling, exit policy)
- Champion/Challenger governance (no live auto-deploy)
- No fixed weights (4 competing algorithms + Meta-Bandit)
- Graceful degradation for Redis, MT5, broker

## DATA RULES
- Real Data >= 95%
- Synthetic Data = 0%
- Coverage >= 95%
- Quality Score >= 90/100
- Each source stored separately: titan/data/sources/{source}/

## CODE RULES
- Python 3.12, type hints (PEP 604 style: str | None)
- Test every new feature (364+ tests, 0 regressions)
- Run: PYTHONPATH=/home/z/my-project python -m pytest titan/tests/ -q --tb=no
- Skip test_database.py + test_infrastructure.py (need structlog)

## REPORT STYLE (Goldman Sachs White Paper)
- Navy: #14213D | Crimson: #C8102E | Gold: #B8860B
- Green: #1E7D3A (PASS) | Red: #C8102E (FAIL)
- Fonts: Liberation Serif (body), Liberation Sans (headings), Liberation Mono (code)
- Page breaks: only between cover/TOC/body

## DUKASCOPY DOWNLOAD
- .bi5 = LZMA compressed, BIG-ENDIAN binary
- Tick = 20 bytes: int32 ts_ms, int32 ASK, int32 BID, float32 ask_vol, float32 bid_vol
- URL month = 0-indexed (Jan=00)
- Price scale = 1000
- Rate limit: ~4 sec/day, use timeout 300, 2-week batches
- Resume: skip already-downloaded days

## KEY FILES
- PROJECT_CONTEXT.md — Master map (READ FIRST)
- project_memory.md — Detailed memory
- worklog.md — Session log (append-only)
- titan/ — Main codebase (12,169 lines, 22 modules)
- titan/data/sources/dukascopy/daily/ — REAL M1 data (783,085 bars)
- scripts/real_data/fast_download.py — Dukascopy downloader
- download/ — Deliverables (26 PDF, 22 DOCX, 3 JSON, 3 ZIP)

## CURRENT PHASE
Real Data Acquisition Audit — downloading REAL Dukascopy XAUUSD M1 data.
783,085 bars downloaded (31 months). Missing: 2020 (most), 2021 (all), 2022 H2.
Next: finish downloads, generate audit reports, output REAL DATA VERIFIED or DATA REJECTED.
